import { StatusBar } from 'expo-status-bar';
import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react';
import { StyleSheet, Text, View, Button, Image, ScrollView, FlatList } from 'react-native';

export default function Aboutus({ navigation }) {

  return (
    <ScrollView>

      <View style={styles.container}>
        <StatusBar style="auto" />
        <View style={styles.Heading}>
          <Text h1>About Us</Text>
        </View>

        <View style={styles.whoAreWe}>

          <Text h3>Who are we?</Text>
          <Text>CryptofyHub is a digital currency platform. Userâ€™s can check up-to-date digital currency prices.
            Coinspot is the most up to date and intuitive digital currency platform where users can check for latest digital currency rates.</Text>
        </View>


        <View style={styles.ourFeatures}>
          <Text h3>Our Features</Text>
          <FlatList
            data={[
              { key: 'Trending Top 7 Cryptos' },
              { key: 'Display list of most popular digital currency' },
              { key: 'Search Digital currency from the list of all existing currency' },
              { key: 'Display details of individual currency' },
              { key: 'Current price' },
              { key: 'Market cap' },
              { key: 'Current value' },
              { key: 'Graph/chart with 24 hr prices' },
              { key: 'FAQ for beginners' },
            ]}
            renderItem={({ item }) => <Text style={styles.ourFeatures}>{item.key}</Text>}
          />
        </View>

        <View style={styles.developers}>
          <Text h3>The Developers</Text>
          <FlatList
            data={[
              { key: 'Trending Top 7 Cryptos' },
              { key: 'Display list of most popular digital currency' },
              { key: 'Search Digital currency from the list of all existing currency' },
              { key: 'Display details of individual currency' },
              { key: 'Current price' },
              { key: 'Market cap' },
              { key: 'Current value' },
              { key: 'Graph/chart with 24 hr prices' },
              { key: 'FAQ for beginners' },
            ]}
            renderItem={({ item }) => <Text style={styles.item}>{item.key}</Text>}
          />
        </View>

      </View>
    </ScrollView>

  );
}


const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  container: {
    flex: 1,
    backgroundColor: '#fff',
    alignItems: 'center',
    justifyContent: 'center',
  },
})
